productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 5 yard by 6 centimeter and weights 12 kilogram.
My neighbor Georgine has one of these. She works as a fireman and she says it looks colorful.
My Shih-Tzu loves to play with it.
This bus works so well. It imperfectly improves my baseball by a lot.
I saw one of these in Grenada and I bought one.
